WEBVTT

00:03:28.998 --> 00:03:30.643
Kjo ndodh sepse, kur flitet per ushqime,

00:03:30.643 --> 00:03:33.077
gjate evolucionit truri u mesua 
t'i kushtonte vemendje te vecante

00:03:33.077 --> 00:03:34.955
shijeve te reja ose te ndryshme.

00:03:34.955 --> 00:03:35.900
Pse?

00:03:35.900 --> 00:03:37.070
Ka dy arsye:

00:03:37.070 --> 00:03:39.444
e para, per te kuptuar nese ushqimi ishte apo jo i prishur.

00:03:39.444 --> 00:03:41.731
e dyta, sepse sa me shume varietet

00:03:41.731 --> 00:03:42.753
te kemi ne dieten tone,

00:03:42.753 --> 00:03:43.840
aq me e lehte do te jete

00:03:43.840 --> 00:03:45.876
qe te marrim gjithe lendet qe na duhen.

00:03:45.876 --> 00:03:47.251
Ne menyre qe t'a mbajme te gjalle kete varietet,

00:03:47.251 --> 00:03:49.663
duhet te jemi ne gjendje te dallojme nje ushqim te ri,

00:03:49.663 --> 00:03:50.839
dhe c'ka eshte me e rendesishme,

00:03:50.839 --> 00:03:53.544
duhet te kemi gjithnje deshiren 
per te ngrene ushqime te reja.

00:03:53.544 --> 00:03:55.505
Ja pse niveli i dopamines bie

00:03:55.505 --> 00:03:57.367
kur ushqimi behet i merzitshem.

00:03:57.367 --> 00:03:58.966
Tani le te kthehemi tek vakti jone.

00:03:58.966 --> 00:04:00.423
Cfare ndodh nese ne vend